21/07/2006
SOFIA, Bulgaria -- A joint operation of the Bulgarian National Service for the Fight Against Organised Crime (NSFOC) and the FBI has resulted in unveiling a criminal scheme for drug trafficking and money laundering, NSFOC Commissioner Vanyo Tanov said Thursday (20 July). 
The 34-year old boss of the criminal gang has been arrested in Miami, he noted. 
The investigation on the case lasted almost two years. 
(Sega - 21/07/06; Mediapool - 20/07/06)
